    {
      "id": "PopularPost280389",
      "post_content": "This plus [Elbrus, The Binding Blade](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Elbrus, The Binding Blade); you sneak in a weenie attacker and pop Elbrus in with the Stonehewer right before damage is dealt. Poof, instant 13/13 demon.   \n  \nOr you could use a [Quietus Spike](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Quietus Spike), strip away 1/2 their life.   \n  \nLastly, another great one is slip [Sword of Kaldra](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Sword of Kaldra) onto a blocked (or blocking) creature, and send their creature tumbling into oblivion. You could even do this on purpose with a provoke creature.  \n  \n5/5, so overpowered.",
      "posted_by": "KadanJoelavich",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost280389\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_post\">This plus <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Elbrus, The Binding Blade\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Elbrus, The Binding Blade\">Elbrus, The Binding Blade</a>; you sneak in a weenie attacker and pop Elbrus in with the Stonehewer right before damage is dealt. Poof, instant 13/13 demon. <br/><br/>Or you could use a <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Quietus Spike\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Quietus Spike\">Quietus Spike</a>, strip away 1/2 their life. <br/><br/>Lastly, another great one is slip <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Sword of Kaldra\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Sword of Kaldra\">Sword of Kaldra</a> onto a blocked (or blocking) creature, and send their creature tumbling into oblivion. You could even do this on purpose with a provoke creature.<br/><br/>5/5, so overpowered.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '280389'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy89883\">KadanJoelavich</span>\r\n                                (11/7/2012 6:28:42 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n 