    {
      "id": "PopularPost231338",
      "post_content": "An amazing card. You can use it during combat to equip him or another monster with an equipment before damage is declared. Say you swing with this guy: Your opponent can choose to chump block, in which case you tap him and grab a [Loxodon Warhammer](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Loxodon Warhammer), block with something bigger, in which case you grab say [Shield of Kaldra](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Shield of Kaldra) or [Runechanted Pike](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Runechanted Pike), or they could let him through, in which case you can grab [Worldslayer](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Worldslayer) or [Grafted Exoskeleton](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Grafted Exoskeleton).  \n  \nHowever, my favorite card to equip him with is [Umbral Mantle](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Umbral Mantle). Assuming you have a lot of mana, you can equip multiple cards from your deck *in combat*. Equipping just the Mantle and Grafted Exoskeleton is 8 poison, possibly game if you can kick Mantle twice. If they block, equip with both the [Shield of Kaldra](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Shield of Kaldra) and the [Sword of Kaldra](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Sword of Kaldra) to exile the blocker. The possibilities are endless. 5... [(see all)](javascript:void(0);)",
      "posted_by": "Kelptic183",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost231338\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_post\">An amazing card. You can use it during combat to equip him or another monster with an equipment before damage is declared. Say you swing with this guy: Your opponent can choose to chump block, in which case you tap him and grab a <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Loxodon Warhammer\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Loxodon Warhammer\">Loxodon Warhammer</a>, block with something bigger, in which case you grab say <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Shield of Kaldra\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Shield of Kaldra\">Shield of Kaldra</a> or <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Runechanted Pike\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Runechanted Pike\">Runechanted Pike</a>, or they could let him through, in which case you can grab <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Worldslayer\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Worldslayer\">Worldslayer</a> or <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Grafted Exoskeleton\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Grafted Exoskeleton\">Grafted Exoskeleton</a>.<br/><br/>However, my favorite card to equip him with is <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Umbral Mantle\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Umbral Mantle\">Umbral Mantle</a>. Assuming you have a lot of mana, you can equip multiple cards from your deck <i>in combat</i>. Equipping just the Mantle and Grafted Exoskeleton is 8 poison, possibly game if you can kick Mantle twice. If they block, equip with both the <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Shield of Kaldra\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Shield of Kaldra\">Shield of Kaldra</a> and the <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Sword of Kaldra\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Sword of Kaldra\">Sword of Kaldra</a> to exile the blocker. The possibilities are endless. 5... <a href=\"javascript:void(0);\" onclick=\"ExpandPost(event, this, 231338)\">(see all)</a></span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '231338'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy76151\">Kelptic183</span>\r\n                                (3/4/2012 8:43:01 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"5.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/>\n<br/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRat